headline: 2 Industrials Stocks with Promising Prospects and 1 We Find Risky
summary: Even if they go mostly unnoticed, industrial businesses are the backbone of our country. Sure, they are at the whim of macroeconomic factors that influence capital spending (like interest rates), but the industry has held its ground over the past six months as its 4.6% return was almost identical to the S&P 500.
